      </p>
    </header>

    <nav class="links">
      <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/rishimullur" class="link-item" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <span class="link-icon">üíº</span>
        <span class="link-text">LinkedIn</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://twitter.com/rishimullur" class="link-item" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <span class="link-icon">ùïè</span>
